**Overview**

This mod is a universal required dependency for the "Copper Carved Company" series of mods (such as Jerotes Village v1.1.5+). Some features have been moved here to improve compatibility between various mods.

Open source, anyone can create extensions for this series.![Replace this with a description](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/023632b16b28c8fa695d05a5e95706803aef40ad.png)![Exploration Eye]

**Content**

- Certain javelin-type items and beast-armor-type items originally from Jerotes Village have been moved here;
- Restored the spear-type items from version 1.21.1;
- Debugging test creatures, the Creative Claw, and the Exploration Eye;
- When certain creatures have an inventory, they can use bows, crossbows, tridents, throwables, arrows, etc., from their inventory and switch items from it—making them "omni-capable creatures." As of mod version 1.2.3, they can also use firearms from the TACZ mod;
- Two-handed weapons that can block, suitable for polearm-type weapons used on foot (pikes), as well as hammer-type and dagger-type weapons;
- Items that apply buffs when any creature holds them and attacks;
- Universal datapack tags that will be used across Jerotes-created mods, e.g., "jerotes:humanoid";
- And more...
